-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_absence_cdl`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_absence_cdl` (
  `code_absence` int(10) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `comptabilise` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `n_comptabilise` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `n_incomptabilise` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `date` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  `jeton` varchar(3) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `horaire` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nombre` smallint(6) NOT NULL default '0',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `session` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_absence`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_inscription_2` (`code_inscription`,`annee_academique`,`session`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=3784 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_absence_pri`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_absence_pri` (
  `code_absence` int(10) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `comptabilise` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `n_comptabilise` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `n_incomptabilise` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `date` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  `jeton` varchar(3) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `horaire` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nombre` smallint(6) NOT NULL default '0',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `session` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_absence`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_inscription_2` (`code_inscription`,`annee_academique`,`session`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_absence_pri`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_actualite`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_actualite` (
  `code_actualite` tinyint(3) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `titre` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `contenu` text collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `date` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  `type` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_actualite`),
  KEY `type` (`type`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=41 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_admin`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_admin` (
  `id_user` tinyint(4) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `nom` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `prenom` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `email` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `menu` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `last_acces` datetime NOT NULL default '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `ip` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `login` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `mot_pass` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id_user`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=10 ;

-- Dumping data for table `tbl_admin`

-- Table structure for table `tbl_appreciation`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_appreciation` (
  `code_appreciation` mediumint(9) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `semestre` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `appreciation` text NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_appreciation`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 AUTO_INCREMENT=1193 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_bac`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_bac` (
  `id` tinyint(4) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `titre` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=7 ;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_bac`
--

INSERT INTO `tbl_bac` (`id`, `titre`, `archive`) VALUES
(1, 'Litraire', '0'),
(2, 'Scientifique', '0'),
(3, 'Economique', '0'),
(4, 'Technique', '0'),
(5, 'Equivalence', '0');

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_buletin`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_buletin` (
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `cours` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `sem` varchar(6) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `note` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `credit` varchar(3) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `semestre` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`,`semestre`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

-- Table structure for table `tbl_compta`

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_compta` (
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',

  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_inscription`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_cours`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_cours` (
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `titre` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `titre_eng` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nbr_credit` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `session` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `semestre` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_prof` smallint(6) NOT NULL default '0',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0000',
  `inscription` binary(1) NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  `type` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  KEY `code_prof` (`code_prof`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

-- Dumping data for table `tbl_cours`
--

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_cours_cdl`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_cours_cdl` (
  `annee` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nom` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `prenom` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date_naissance` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nationalite` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `adresse` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `sexe` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_bac1` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_bac2` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `serie_bac` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `tel` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `email` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `filiere` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `lieu_naissance` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `cin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `financeur` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `last_diplome` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `cinq_photo` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `copie_bac` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `buletin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `copie_cin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `extrait_naissance` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `test_fr` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `test_eng` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `aquise_academique` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `login` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `mot_pass` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `acces` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `last_acces` datetime NOT NULL default '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `adresse_ip` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `etat` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `activite` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `annee_inscription` year(4) NOT NULL default '0000',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `annee` (`annee`,`code_inscription`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_cours_cdl`
--

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_cours_pri`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_cours_pri` (
  `annee` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nom` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `prenom` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date_naissance` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nationalite` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `adresse` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `sexe` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_bac1` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_bac2` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `serie_bac` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `tel` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `email` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `filiere` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `lieu_naissance` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `cin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `financeur` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `last_diplome` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `cinq_photo` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `copie_bac` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `buletin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `copie_cin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `extrait_naissance` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `test_fr` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `test_eng` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `aquise_academique` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `login` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `mot_pass` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `acces` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `last_acces` datetime NOT NULL default '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `adresse_ip` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `etat` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `activite` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `annee_inscription` year(4) NOT NULL default '0000',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `annee` (`annee`,`code_inscription`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

-- Dumping data for table `tbl_cours_pri`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_cv`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_cv` (
  `id` mediumint(9) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `nom` varchar(120) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `email` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `tel` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `diplome` text collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `commentaire` text collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `matiere` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=104 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_demande`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_demande` (
  `code_demande` int(10) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `nom_prenom` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  `objet` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `explication` text collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `reponse` text collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `reponse1` text collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `code_prof` tinyint(3) unsigned NOT NULL default '0',
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_demande`),
  KEY `code_prof` (`code_prof`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `objet` (`objet`),
  KEY `date` (`date`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=125 ;

-- Dumping data for table `tbl_demande`
--

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_descriptif`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_descriptif` (
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `competence` text collate utf8_unicode_ci,
  `connaissance` text collate utf8_unicode_ci,
  `contenu` text collate utf8_unicode_ci,
  `methode` text collate utf8_unicode_ci,
  `exigence` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `pourcentage` text collate utf8_unicode_ci,
  `bibliographie` text collate utf8_unicode_ci,
  `attitude` text collate utf8_unicode_ci,
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0'
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_descriptif`
--

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_document`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_document` (
  `id` mediumint(4) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `nom` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `titre` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `processus` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `groupe` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=21 ;

-- Dumping data for table `tbl_document`
--

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_empreinte`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_empreinte` (
  `code_emprunt` mediumint(9) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `code_livre` int(25) NOT NULL default '0',
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0',
  `code_prof` tinyint(3) NOT NULL default '0',
  `date_empreint` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  `date_retour` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  `retourne` binary(1) NOT NULL default '1',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_emprunt`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=5 ;

-- Dumping data for table `tbl_empreinte`

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_etudiant`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_etudiant` (
  `annee` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nom` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `prenom` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date_naissance` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nationalite` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `adresse` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `sexe` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_bac1` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_bac2` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `serie_bac` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `tel` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `email` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `filiere` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `lieu_naissance` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `cin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `financeur` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `last_diplome` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `cinq_photo` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `copie_bac` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `buletin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `copie_cin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `extrait_naissance` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `test_fr` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `test_eng` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `aquise_academique` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `login` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `mot_pass` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `acces` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `last_acces` datetime NOT NULL default '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `adresse_ip` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `etat` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `activite` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `annee` (`annee`,`code_inscription`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_etudiant_cdl`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_etudiant_cdl` (
  `annee` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nom` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `prenom` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date_naissance` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nationalite` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `adresse` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `sexe` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_bac1` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_bac2` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `serie_bac` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `tel` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `email` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `filiere` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `lieu_naissance` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `cin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `financeur` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `last_diplome` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `cinq_photo` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `copie_bac` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `buletin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `copie_cin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `extrait_naissance` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `test_fr` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `test_eng` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `aquise_academique` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `login` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `mot_pass` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `acces` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `last_acces` datetime NOT NULL default '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `adresse_ip` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `etat` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `activite` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `annee` (`annee`,`code_inscription`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_etudiant_cdl`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_etudiant_cdl1`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_etudiant_cdl1` (
  `email` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nom` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `tel` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `adresse` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `langue` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default ''
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

-- Table structure for table `tbl_etudiant_pri`

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_etudiant_pri` (
  `annee` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nom` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `prenom` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date_naissance` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nationalite` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `adresse` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `sexe` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_bac1` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_bac2` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `serie_bac` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `tel` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `email` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `filiere` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `lieu_naissance` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `cin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `financeur` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `last_diplome` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `cinq_photo` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `copie_bac` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `buletin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `copie_cin` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `extrait_naissance` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `test_fr` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `test_eng` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `aquise_academique` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `login` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `mot_pass` varchar(150) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `acces` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `last_acces` datetime NOT NULL default '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `adresse_ip` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `etat` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `activite` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `annee` (`annee`,`code_inscription`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_inscription_cours`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_inscription_cours` (
  `id` mediumint(9) unsigned NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0',
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0',
  `date_inscription` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  `liste_attente` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0000',
  `session` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id`),
  KEY `session` (`session`),
  KEY `annee_academique` (`annee_academique`),
  KEY `code_cours` (`code_cours`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_cours_2` (`code_cours`,`code_inscription`,`annee_academique`,`session`),
  KEY `code_inscription_2` (`code_inscription`,`annee_academique`,`session`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=1088 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_inscription_cours_cdl`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_inscription_cours_cdl` (
  `id` mediumint(9) unsigned NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0',
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0',
  `date_inscription` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  `liste_attente` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0000',
  `session` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id`),
  KEY `session` (`session`),
  KEY `annee_academique` (`annee_academique`),
  KEY `code_cours` (`code_cours`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_cours_2` (`code_cours`,`code_inscription`,`annee_academique`,`session`),
  KEY `code_inscription_2` (`code_inscription`,`annee_academique`,`session`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_inscription_cours_cdl`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_inscription_cours_pri`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_inscription_cours_pri` (
  `id` mediumint(9) unsigned NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0',
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0',
  `date_inscription` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  `liste_attente` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0000',
  `session` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id`),
  KEY `session` (`session`),
  KEY `annee_academique` (`annee_academique`),
  KEY `code_cours` (`code_cours`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_cours_2` (`code_cours`,`code_inscription`,`annee_academique`,`session`),
  KEY `code_inscription_2` (`code_inscription`,`annee_academique`,`session`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_inscription_cours_pri`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_inscription_session`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_inscription_session` (
  `id` smallint(6) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `code_cours` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `inscrit_printemps` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `inscrit_automne` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id`),
  KEY `code_cours` (`code_cours`),
  KEY `annee_academique` (`annee_academique`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 AUTO_INCREMENT=201 ;

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_note`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_note` (
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `controle1` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `examen_mi_semestre` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `controle3` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `examen_final` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `participation` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `devoirs_projets` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `note_finale_chiffre` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `note_finale_lettre` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `observation` text collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `note_finale1` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `code_note` smallint(6) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `nbr_absence` smallint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `n_comptabilise` tinyint(2) NOT NULL default '0',
  `n_incomptabilise` tinyint(2) NOT NULL default '0',
  `point_fort` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `point_ameliorer` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0000',
  `session` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  `nfo` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `nlo` varchar(3) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nco` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_note`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_cours` (`code_cours`),
  KEY `session` (`session`),
  KEY `annee_academique` (`annee_academique`),
  KEY `code_inscription_2` (`code_inscription`,`annee_academique`,`session`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=1085 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_note_cdl`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_note_cdl` (
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `controle1` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `examen_mi_semestre` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `controle3` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `examen_final` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `participation` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `devoirs_projets` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `note_finale_chiffre` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `note_finale_lettre` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `observation` text collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `note_finale1` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `code_note` smallint(6) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `nbr_absence` smallint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `n_comptabilise` tinyint(2) NOT NULL default '0',
  `n_incomptabilise` tinyint(2) NOT NULL default '0',
  `point_fort` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `point_ameliorer` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0000',
  `session` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  `nfo` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `nlo` varchar(3) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nco` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_note`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_cours` (`code_cours`),
  KEY `session` (`session`),
  KEY `annee_academique` (`annee_academique`),
  KEY `code_inscription_2` (`code_inscription`,`annee_academique`,`session`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_note_cdl`
--

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_note_pri`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_note_pri` (
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `controle1` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `examen_mi_semestre` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `controle3` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `examen_final` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `participation` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `devoirs_projets` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `note_finale_chiffre` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `note_finale_lettre` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `observation` text collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `note_finale1` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `code_note` smallint(6) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `nbr_absence` smallint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `n_comptabilise` tinyint(2) NOT NULL default '0',
  `n_incomptabilise` tinyint(2) NOT NULL default '0',
  `point_fort` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `point_ameliorer` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '0000',
  `session` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  `nfo` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  `nlo` varchar(3) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `nco` varchar(5) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '-',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_note`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`),
  KEY `code_cours` (`code_cours`),
  KEY `session` (`session`),
  KEY `annee_academique` (`annee_academique`),
  KEY `code_inscription_2` (`code_inscription`,`annee_academique`,`session`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_note_pri`

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_paiement`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_paiement` (
  `id_paiement` mediumint(9) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `session` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `montant` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `type_paiement` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date_paiement` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  `numero_cheque` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `banque` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `date_retirer` date default NULL,
  `validation` binary(1) default NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id_paiement`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_paiement`

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_professeur`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_professeur` (
  `code_prof` tinyint(3) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `nom_prenom` varchar(100) NOT NULL default '',
  `nationnalite` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `diplome` varchar(100) NOT NULL default '',
  `matiere` varchar(100) NOT NULL default '',
  `mail` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `contact` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `niveau` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `type` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `login` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `mot_pass` varchar(150) NOT NULL default '',
  `last_acces` datetime NOT NULL default '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  `adresse_ip` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `menu_acces` binary(1) NOT NULL default '',
  `heure` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `commentaire` text NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_prof`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 AUTO_INCREMENT=47 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_professeur_cdl`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_professeur_cdl` (
  `code_prof` tinyint(3) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `nom_prenom` varchar(100) NOT NULL default '',
  `nationnalite` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `diplome` varchar(100) NOT NULL default '',
  `matiere` varchar(100) NOT NULL default '',
  `mail` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `contact` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `niveau` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `type` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `login` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `mot_pass` varchar(150) NOT NULL default '',
  `last_acces` datetime NOT NULL default '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  `adresse_ip` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `menu_acces` binary(1) NOT NULL default '',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_prof`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_professeur_cdl`
--


-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_professeur_pri`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_professeur_pri` (
  `code_prof` tinyint(3) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `nom_prenom` varchar(100) NOT NULL default '',
  `nationnalite` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `diplome` varchar(100) NOT NULL default '',
  `matiere` varchar(100) NOT NULL default '',
  `mail` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `contact` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `niveau` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `type` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `login` varchar(50) NOT NULL default '',
  `mot_pass` varchar(150) NOT NULL default '',
  `last_acces` datetime NOT NULL default '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  `adresse_ip` varchar(25) NOT NULL default '',
  `menu_acces` binary(1) NOT NULL default '',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_prof`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 AUTO_INCREMENT=1 ;

--
-- Dumping data for table `tbl_professeur_pri`
--

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_professor_menu`

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_professor_menu` (
  `id` tinyint(4) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `title` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `link` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `publie` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `ordre` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `archive` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=8 ;

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_seance`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_seance` (
  `code_seance` smallint(10) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `jours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `jours1` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `horaire` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `horaire1` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `salle` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `salle1` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `session` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `annee_academique` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `code_prof` mediumint(9) NOT NULL default '0',
  `nbr_inscrit` tinyint(3) unsigned NOT NULL default '0',
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_seance`),
  KEY `code_cours` (`code_cours`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=99 ;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_situation_financier`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_situation_financier` (
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `replicat` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `frais_etude_dossier` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `f_date` date default NULL,
  `frais_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `f_i_date` date default NULL,
  `cheque` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `cheque_date` date default NULL,
  `espece` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `espece_date` date default NULL,
  `reste` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci default NULL,
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_sondage`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_sondage` (
  `id_sondage` tinyint(3) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `code_inscription` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `objet` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `conseil` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `choix` varchar(100) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `date` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id_sondage`),
  KEY `code_inscription` (`code_inscription`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=23 ;

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_student_menu`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_student_menu` (
  `id` tinyint(4) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `title` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `link` varchar(50) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `publie` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `ordre` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `archive` tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  `checkout` date NOT NULL default '0000-00-00',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=16 ;

--
-- Table structure for table `tbl_syllabus`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tbl_syllabus` (
  `code_cours` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `week` varchar(25) collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL default '',
  `contenu` text collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `avancement` text collate utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `code_sylabus` mediumint(11) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  `archive` binary(1) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (`code_sylabus`),
  KEY `code_cours` (`code_cours`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM  DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci AUTO_INCREMENT=2391 ;
